<tr>
  <td>
        <h4>Generic Topic Fields</h4>
        <p>All topic types are descended from the generic "Topic" which can not have it form fields changed.  They are the following:
        <ul>
                <li>Title: What shoule we this topic?  This will also be used to generate a URL for this topic.</li>
                <li>Short Summary: This is a brief blurb suitable for lists of results.  It should be plain text.</li>
                <li>Description: Describe the topic.  This where we store the history of the topic we are writing about. TODO: flesh out description of this attribute.</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <p>These form fields will be present in all other topics, no matter what topic type they fall under.</p>
  </td>
</tr>